Firestrike, currently busy trying to crimple Prowls legs, was hit by 
the shots, loosening his grip slightly, while his armour was dented.  
On his shoulder a small gun pivoted.  "Because cowards shall die," 
he yelled.  Two grenades were fired out of the gun at Alpha Dolphy.
